# E-commerce UI Clone (HTML & CSS)

This is my first web development project where I created a static clone of the Amazon homepage using only HTML and CSS.

The main goal of this project was to understand page structure, layout design, and basic styling techniques.

## Features
- Static Amazon homepage layout
- Header, navigation bar, product sections, and footer
- Built using HTML5 and CSS3
- Desktop-focused design

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- GitHub Pages

## Live Demo
https://nayan-create-cyber.github.io/E-commerce-Clone/

## Learning Outcome
- Improved understanding of HTML structure
- Learned CSS layout techniques using Flexbox
- Gained experience in hosting static websites using GitHub Pages

## Future Improvements
- Make the website responsive
- Add mobile and tablet support
- Improve UI consistency

## Disclaimer
This project is created for learning and educational purposes only.  
All images and design inspiration belong to Amazon.
